{
  "texts": [
    "AI-CI-AI literacy concept inventory assessment 33.",
    "AI-CI is a performance-based concept inventory scale for middle school students assessing AI-related knowledge through 20 multiple-choice questions.",
    "The authors used their own AI literacy curriculum 59 to design the scale's content.",
    "IRT was used for validation.",
    "There is good evidence for the scale's content validity and structural validity, and high evidence for the scale's internal consistency and responsiveness."
  ]
}